title: Shakira - Can't  Forget You ft. Rihanna.mp3
description:
Shakira and Rihanna have come together for the former's new music video "Can't Remember to Forget You," and the end result is sexy to say the least!

With these two seductive stars - neither of whom need a surname, they're so sultry - teaming up, you knew this buzzed-about collaboration would be hot.

from Shakira's forthcoming album "Shakira", available March 25
